<li>Fowles, G. R. and Cassiday, G. L. <i>Analytical Mechanics</i> (6ed). Saunders College Publishing, 1999. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0030223172" class="internal">ISBN 0-03-022317-2</a></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFFeynman_R_P.2C_Leighton_R_B_.26_Sands_M2006">Feynman R P, Leighton R B &amp; Sands M (2006). <i><a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/61355214&amp;referer=brief_results" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/61355214&amp;referer=brief_results" rel="nofollow">The Feynman lectures on physics</a></i>. <b>Vol. 1</b>. Pearson/Addison-Wesley. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0805390499" class="internal">ISBN 0805390499</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/61355214&amp;referer=brief_results" class="external free" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/61355214&amp;referer=brief_results" rel="nofollow">http://worldcat.org/oclc/61355214&amp;referer=brief_results</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Feynman+lectures+on+physics&amp;rft.aulast=Feynman+R+P%2C+Leighton+R+B+%26+Sands+M&amp;rft.au=Feynman+R+P%2C+Leighton+R+B+%26+Sands+M&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.volume=Vol.+1&amp;rft.pub=Pearson%2FAddison-Wesley&amp;rft.isbn=0805390499&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fworldcat.org%2Foclc%2F61355214%26referer%3Dbrief_results&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Newton%27s_laws_of_motion"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
